{"tid":1724973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［推到蘋果立場見到］黑衣人=/=示威者=/=抗爭者","createTime":"2019-11-15T15:21:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T15:33:16.000Z","uid":136303,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"259da851c21b6199119227b6827571711330f9f2","tid":1724973,"uid":136303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:21:28.000Z","msg":"首先辛苦哂記者大佬們 你地日以繼夜工作小弟好欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過小弟留意到一樣野 希望記者們可以改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係逢係有示威 所以黑衣人既行為 蘋果同立場都會用&ldquo;示威者&rdquo;或者&ldquo;抗爭者&rdquo;作主語 但有啲行為可能未必係真手足做 例如今晚中大燒車（我並非一口咬定係鬼做 如果係手足做既 我都唔割）但蘋果同立場都會用示威者同抗爭者 咁樣係入哂我地數 但港台通常係用&ldquo;黑衣人&rdquo;黎描述 咁樣 係人係鬼 都係觀眾自己判斷 咁樣會好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望之後改哂用<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑衣人</span></span><br />\n例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gq9odBK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGq9odBK.png&h=7d067bad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8shUkgL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8shUkgL.png&h=ff1259d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auhk0gM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fauhk0gM.png&h=21e8afed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8b8a53ee4e8d649b1356a4fe63773fd875c4c642","tid":1724973,"uid":136303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:22:13.000Z","msg":"推到蘋果立場見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aef4f3ad768d1649eb1e5453860c8737339cc6ee","tid":1724973,"uid":136303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:22:25.000Z","msg":"到蘋果立場見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"989ae4d9c28f53bb0e446077e0417a75d77eef58","tid":1724973,"uid":136303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,